# Psychometric Test Guide

A Machine Learning based Career Prediction and Psychometric Assessment System built using Python and Streamlit.

## Features

- Career Prediction
- Psychometric Assessment
- Top 3 Career Recommendations
- Skill Analysis
- Learning Roadmap
- Performance Charts

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Scikit-Learn
- Matplotlib

